# Once done this will define
#
#  KLT_FOUND - system has KLT
#  KLT_INCLUDE_DIRS - the KLT include directory
#  KLT_LIBRARIES - Link these to use KLT
#  KLT_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using KLT
